					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Based on some of kinch's stuff yeah, that seems to be how it identifies. And yes, we need more bones stuff- it's my favorite character in the group.</p> <blockquote> <p>Bit of a nitpick, but shouldn't this also be tagged gamers-against-weed?</p> </blockquote> <p>Well it did just go up, but I'm not sure. Guide says unambiguous mentions only, and its very brief. I could see it getting the jude tag, but that's up to the tech team, I guess.</p> 
				 	]]>
