				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Damn that's good — robo death machines deserve to transition too. Most of the GAW stuff I've seen has relegated Bones to the impartial-moderator role, so it's nice to see its<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-14412-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> character explored more.</p> <p>Bit of a nitpick, but shouldn't this also be tagged <tt>gamers-against-weed</tt>?</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-14412-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. That's the correct pronoun, yes?</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
